html_file_warning: The Apollo 3.0.2 infectious fraction maps to Lancet Ebola 1.0 parameters 'initialInfectiousDying' (infectious individuals who will die) and 'initialInfectiousSurviving' (infectious individuals who will survive). The location population is used together with the probability of a disease outcome of 'death' from the Apollo 3.0.2 diseaseOutcomesWithProbabilities list to translate the infectious fraction into these two parameters.
